{
  "id": "adv_group_sun_04_02",
  "title": "サニーピース 04 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "星村さんと出会って、アイドルを目指し始めた私は\n歌とダンスのレッスンに通い始めたわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After meeting Hoshimura-san‚ I decided to become an idol\nand started taking singing and dancing lessons",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 8.065283394,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "両親がアイドル好きで理解があったから\n私がやりたいって言ったら応援してくれたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My parents like idols and understanding them‚\nso when I told them I wanted to do it‚ they supported me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.2652834893,
      "endTime": 14.4713832855,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "小学生の頃からオーディションは沢山受けていたわ\nもちろん、現実はそんなに甘くなかったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've been applying to a lot of auditions since I was in elementary school\nOf course‚ the world doesn't work that way…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.6847164472,
      "endTime": 23.288684876799998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "当時はすぐにアイドルデビュー出来ると思ってたのよ\nでも、中学に上がる頃には……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "At the time‚ I thought I'd make my idol debut right away\nBut‚ when I entered middle school…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 23.4886846861,
      "endTime": 31.1830853145,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.2330853145
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.2330853145
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "エントリーナンバー七番！\n佐伯遙子です！　よろしくお願いします！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Entry number seven!\nI'm Haruko Saeki! Nice to meet you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2830853145,
      "endTime": 38.569661394799994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob3",
      "speakerName": "審査員A",
      "speakerNameEn": "審査員A",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-shinsaa001.m4a",
      "text": "はい、よろしくお願いします\nでは早速ですが、課題のダンスを見せて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ nice to meet you\nThen‚ please show us the dance you assigned",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7629945755,
      "endTime": 44.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.6296635309
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "（何度もオーディションに落ちまくって）\n（ようやく今回初めて最終審査まで残れたんだもの）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I've failed so many auditions）\n（but I finally made it to the final round for the first time）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.6296635309,
      "endTime": 52.6864207904,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.8997541427
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "（このチャンスは絶対に逃さない！）\n（持てる力を出し切って、合格してみせるわ！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Don't miss this chance!）\n（I'll do my best‚ and pass!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.8997541427,
      "endTime": 59.7280320167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob3",
      "speakerName": "審査員A",
      "speakerNameEn": "審査員A",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-shinsaa002.m4a",
      "text": "……はい、ありがとうございます。もう結構です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "……Yep‚ thank you. That's enough",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9346986453,
      "endTime": 63.0813649814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.2680317243
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でもまだ途中……\n分かりました……ありがとうございました……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? But I'm still in…\nOkay… thank you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2680317243,
      "endTime": 73.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.9072586059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "（審査を途中で止められるなんて）\n（一体どこが悪かったのかしら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（They stopped the audition halfway through）\n（What exactly went wrong…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.9072586059,
      "endTime": 80.0435341833,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6659.408060800004,
          "startTime": 80.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 80.1
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob3",
      "speakerName": "審査員A",
      "speakerNameEn": "審査員A",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-shinsaa003.m4a",
      "text": "なあ、今の子だが……悪くはないんだが、なんというか\n……初々しさ？　華やかさ？　がないんだよな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ about this girl… not bad‚ but what should I say\n…freshness? …brightness? There was no such thing",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.9568645794,
      "endTime": 90.93333028159999,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14609.802087299997,
          "startTime": 95.5666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.7999908448
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.3333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob2",
      "speakerName": "審査員B",
      "speakerNameEn": "審査員B",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-shinsab001.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな、高校生にしては落ち着き過ぎて……\nえ、中学生？　高校生じゃないのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's true‚ she seems so calm for a high school student…\nWait‚ middle school? Aren't she high school?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.2568589846,
      "endTime": 100.3435263316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.6568655967
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob3",
      "speakerName": "審査員A",
      "speakerNameEn": "審査員A",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob3.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-shinsaa004.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく地味なんだよ。アイドルにはもっと\n特別感がないと。あれじゃ誰の印象にも残らないぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Anyway‚ it's plain. Idols need to have\nsomething more special. This won't leave an impression on anyone",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.6568655967,
      "endTime": 109.4101999282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 109.6235332806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "（会話が全部聞こえてるわよ）\n（地味で印象に残らない、か……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I can hear the whole conversation）\n（Plain and unimpressive…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.6235332806,
      "endTime": 117.0234626133,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 117.223462804
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "（でも……確かに審査員に褒められている子達は何かを）\n（持っている気がする。オーラ？　って言うのかしら？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（But… it's true that the girls who get praised）\n（by the judges had something. Aura? Is that what they're saying?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.223462804,
      "endTime": 127.0384059269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "（見ているこっちもワクワクするような……）\n（目が離せなくなるような、そんなキラキラしたものを）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（It makes the viewer feel excited too…）\n（Something shiny that you can't take your eyes off them）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.2250723838,
      "endTime": 134.52425508489998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.8442531267
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "（ああ、そっか……。これがアイドルになる人が）\n（持っている『才能』ってやつなのかも……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Ahh‚ I see…. Maybe this is what they call）\n（the \"talent\" that people who become idols have…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.8442531267,
      "endTime": 142.5666687011,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "（どうすればあの子達みたいにキラキラ出来るんだろう？）\n（こんな地味な私のままじゃ、絶対にアイドルには……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（How can I shine like those girls?）\n（If I stay this plain‚ I'll never be an idol…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.0050389606,
      "endTime": 153.4039264041,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――その年の年末",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――At the end of that year",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.3172596612,
      "endTime": 155.4172657647,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.4839324313
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 155.4839324313
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "今年もNEXT VENUSグランプリを\n観に来たけど、一年なんてあっという間ね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I came to see the NEXT VENUS Grand Prix again\nthis year‚ but a year passes in the blink of an eye…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 156.450599098,
      "endTime": 162.6375152586,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.837515354
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "この一年……いえ、もう何年も沢山のオーディションを\n受けてきたけど、結局一つも引っかからなかった……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This year… no‚ I've taken so many auditions for\nyears now‚ but I haven't passed a single one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.837515354,
      "endTime": 172.83044652919997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 173.0304465292
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "あ……今、ステージで歌ってるアイドルユニット……\n私がオーディションで落ちたグループだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… the idol unit singing on stage now…\nIt's the group I failed the audition for",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.0304465292,
      "endTime": 181.54643278109998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 181.7597661334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "あの時一緒にオーディションを受けた子が\nこんな大舞台で歌ってるのに、私は何をしているの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The girl who auditioned with me back then\nis singing on such a big stage‚ and what am I doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 181.7597661334,
      "endTime": 189.4666625976,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.8507071175
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "華がない、魅力がない、印象に残らない……\nそんなことばかり散々言われて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have no brightness‚ no charm‚ no impression…\nThat's all I've been told…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.8507071175,
      "endTime": 199.03458487159998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 199.2279182431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "デビューどころか、オーディションにも落ちまくって\n……やっぱり私、アイドルに向いてないのかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I failed so many auditions‚ let alone my debut\n…Maybe‚ I'm not cut out to be an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 199.2279182431,
      "endTime": 208.0836996075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 208.2703663505
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "……あら？　あそこにいる女の人は、もしかして……\n……星村さん？　星村さんですよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Huh? That woman over there is‚ perhaps…\n…Hoshimura-san? It's Hoshimura-san‚ right!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 208.2703663505,
      "endTime": 217.3154234564,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 214
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura001.m4a",
      "text": "えっ？　ええと……ごめんなさい\n前にどこかで会ったかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? Um… sorry\nMaybe we've met somewhere before",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.5087565418,
      "endTime": 224.6554069038,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "小さい頃、迷子になっていたところを助けてもらって\n……って、そんな昔のこと覚えてないですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I was young‚ you helped me when I was lost\n…No‚ don't remember that long ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 224.8420735991,
      "endTime": 233.7666656494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 229.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura002.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、あの時の迷子の女の子……大きくなったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Aha‚ that lost girl from back then… you've grown so much",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 233.9207324661,
      "endTime": 240.00739814419998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 240.2207314489
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "私のこと、覚えていてくれたんですか！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You‚ remember me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 240.2207314489,
      "endTime": 243.5920238493,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 243.8053572017
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura003.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、アイドルになるって目を輝かせていたのを\nよく覚えているわ。今でもアイドルを目指しているの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I remember you saying with your eyes shining that\nyou wanted to be an idol. Are you still aspiring to be an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.8053572017,
      "endTime": 252.6853571254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\n……でも、全然オーディションに受からなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\n…But‚ I never passed any auditions…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.8720238684,
      "endTime": 260.0956064223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "私は地味で、印象に残らないらしいです……\nアイドルには向いてないって、散々言われて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I'm plain and unimpressive…\nI've heard many times that I wasn't cut out to be an idol…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.2889396507,
      "endTime": 269.1915473778,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 269.3782139301
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk026.m4a",
      "text": "私にアイドルなんて無理だったのかなとか……\n諦めた方がいいのかなとか、考えちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If being an idol was difficult for me…\nI'm wondering if it would be better to give up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.3782139301,
      "endTime": 277.2399271487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura004.m4a",
      "text": "そう……みんながそう言うのなら\nアイドルには向いていないのかもしれないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… everyone says that‚\nmaybr you're not cut out to be an idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 277.426593701,
      "endTime": 283.7999493757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 283.9932827472
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk027.m4a",
      "text": "あ……そうですよね……\nやっぱり私、アイドルには……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… I guess so…\nAs expected‚ I wasn't cut out…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 283.9932827472,
      "endTime": 291.5451605319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 291.7451605319
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura005.m4a",
      "text": "……で、それがどうしたの？　向いていないから何？\n向いてる人しかアイドルを目指しちゃいけないの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…And‚ So what? So what I'm not cut out?\nShould only those who are cut out to be an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.7451605319,
      "endTime": 300.0918352603,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 300.2785020033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk028.m4a",
      "text": "え……でも……\n向いていないのに、アイドルになれる訳……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… But…\nI'm not cut out‚ but how can I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 300.2785020033,
      "endTime": 306.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura006.m4a",
      "text": "私も若い頃はよく言われたわ\nお前には才能がない、アイドルには向いてないって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was often told when I was younger\nYou have no talent‚ you're not cut out to be an idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 306.4825134594,
      "endTime": 313.5558508235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 313.8158651033
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura007.m4a",
      "text": "それでも……向いてないって何度言われても\n諦めなかったから、私は夢を掴めたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… No matter how many times I was told I wasn't cut out for it‚\nI never gave up‚ and I was able to achieve my dream",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 313.8158651033,
      "endTime": 322.1025217691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura008.m4a",
      "text": "向いているかどうかよりも、大事なのは\n自分を信じられるか……想いを貫けるかどうかよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "More important than whether you're cut out for it\nIs being able to believe in yourself… and stick to your guns",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 322.3158549308,
      "endTime": 330.5825540542,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 330.7825541496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk029.m4a",
      "text": "自分を信じる……想いを貫く……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Believe in yourself… stick to your guns…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 330.7825541496,
      "endTime": 335.3896062851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 335.5896063805
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk030.m4a",
      "text": "……ごめんなさい。私、ちょっと思い通りに\nいかないからって弱気になってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm sorry. I'm a little weak\nbecause things didn't go as planned",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 335.5896063805,
      "endTime": 343.1328262329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 343.3194930713
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk031.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルに大事なのは\n負けない心、挫けない心、諦めない心……ですよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's important for an idol is\nwon't lose‚ doesn't get frustrated‚ and doesn't give up… right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 343.3194930713,
      "endTime": 352.2555251757,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 352.4688586235
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk032.m4a",
      "text": "星村さんはそうやってトップアイドルになったんですね\nだったら私も、星村さんのように……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's how Hoshimura-san became a top idol\nSo I'll be like Hoshimura-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 352.4688586235,
      "endTime": 360.6262838364,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 360.8129503887
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk033.m4a",
      "text": "星村さんみたいに自分を信じて、想いを貫いて\n私らしいアイドルになってみせます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like Hoshimura-san‚ believe in myself‚ stick to my guns\nand try to become an idol that's true to myself!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 360.8129503887,
      "endTime": 369.0375309627,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk034.m4a",
      "text": "もう絶対に諦めません！\nトップアイドル目指して、これからも頑張ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll never give up anymore!\nI'll keep working hard‚ to become a top idol!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 369.2508641243,
      "endTime": 375.5333211263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 375.8468025843
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura009.m4a",
      "text": "……キラキラ輝く、いい目をしているわね\n初めて会った時も感じた、私の好きな目よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…You have beautiful‚ shining eyes\nI felt that the first time we met‚ they're my favorite eyes",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 375.8468025843,
      "endTime": 384.0334531465,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura010.m4a",
      "text": "諦めずに頑張って\nあなたならきっと、素敵なアイドルになれるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't give up‚ keep working hard\nI'm sure‚ you'll become a wonderful idol",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 384.2467863082,
      "endTime": 390.106786251,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 390.3134529749
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk035.m4a",
      "text": "はい！\nよーし、すぐに帰って次のオーディションを探すわよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes!\nOkay‚ I'll go home right away and look for the next audition~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 390.3134529749,
      "endTime": 396.3217297236,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 396.5350629806
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura011.m4a",
      "text": "オーディション……\nそういえば、あなたは星見市に住んでいたわよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Audition…\nBy the way‚ you lived in Hoshimi City‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 396.5350629806,
      "endTime": 402.38171339030004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hrk036.m4a",
      "text": "え？　そうですけど……どうして知ってるんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes? That's true but… how did you know?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 402.5683800379,
      "endTime": 408.0199222246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 408.2265887577
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura012.m4a",
      "text": "迷子になって泣いているあなたから、名前と住所を\n聞き出すのに苦労したから、印象に残っているわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I had a hard time getting your name and address while you\nwere lost and crying‚ so it left a lasting impression on me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 408.2265887577,
      "endTime": 415.5666605632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura013.m4a",
      "text": "……これも縁かもしれないわね。実は知り合いが\n星見市で新たに芸能プロダクションを立ち上げるのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…This might be fate. Actually‚ an acquaintance of mine is\nstarting a new entertainment production company in Hoshimi City.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 415.959938367,
      "endTime": 425.1922286349,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_arenaseats-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "arenaseats-00-noon",
      "startTime": 425.3599159876
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "wmob2",
      "speakerName": "星村恵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Hoshimura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-wmob2.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02/sud_vo_adv_group_sun_04_02-hoshimura014.m4a",
      "text": "小さな芸能事務所で、所属アイドルはまだいないけど\n……興味があるなら紹介しましょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a small agency‚ and doesn't have any idols yet\n…If you're interested‚ can I introduce you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 425.3599159876,
      "endTime": 432.9333292644,
      "sfxList": []
    }
